<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/clinical-trials-a-significant-part-of-cancer-care/">Clinical trials: A significant part of cancer care</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
